{"tid":299774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（急）請教各位巴絲如何拒絕呀媽煮飯？","createTime":"2017-06-27T10:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T00:39:28.000Z","uid":107294,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"961c2bd2e40cf828061a6ea06f4d1a13cfed3a84","tid":299774,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:48:03.000Z","msg":"講真 我呀媽煮野真係唔得 <br />\n佢都有返工係一個禮拜煮二三日<br />\n試過阻止 話外賣啦 你咪煮啦<br />\n之後後果就當然佢發好大脾氣<br />\n成個月比佢係咁唸經 話我不孝 佢死左屎都無得食<br />\n想請教各位巴絲如何拒絕呀媽煮飯帶婉轉同唔不孝？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935a3135d37658a090c56f7b2a2c81b9454e06f7","tid":299774,"uid":61571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:49:37.000Z","msg":"請工人"},{"pid":"8dc64b3c094e9bd74b086914b1b70154018a76fe","tid":299774,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:50:26.000Z","msg":"教佢煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c454158ea4ceeac21388dc7b675a8772a61aa153","tid":299774,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請工人</blockquote><br />\n小妹中六畢業 返得兩日pt 無能力"},{"pid":"8aff8fe6796aa3e770ad0f64b989a96ab77265dc","tid":299774,"uid":7824,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:51:57.000Z","msg":"係佢面前倒左啲飯餸 之前佢仲要跪係到眼濕濕執返 <br />\n扮撚哂野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf610df9528f8071cfc7754a27a4c5f71fe9c21","tid":299774,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教佢煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點夠薑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad665626c87d2ae71c86666d2f69c241038b6efd","tid":299774,"