ckquote><br />\nGood"},{"pid":"f021b9a1bde3c0900c8a674883fc51592aae591c","tid":299774,"uid":40718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T11:53:03.000Z","msg":"直接講話難食咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7fa58de2ef619d03aaa2ae14a77943f2418609","tid":299774,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T11:55:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接講話難食咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一段已經講左"},{"pid":"40bed0269bcaaf95316f2b3e381ae0aade0a824a","tid":299774,"uid":50621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T11:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>請好好珍惜有住家飯你食嘅日子</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我呀媽係真係唔識煮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但又自我滿足個類</blockquote><br />\n我明<br />\n我真係明</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 事實上佢煮完都唔多食 話廚房煮太耐 好熱 叫我食</blockquote><br />\n一人一啖<br />\n餵佢食"},{"pid":"1a22ad8336c35fe01d7a2662c4c3ae5af65a8b1a","tid":299774,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:00:22.000Z","msg":"話加班唔返黎食，唔好留飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d28217fb2dfd09a460a143999bdb334c69b423e","tid":299774,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:00:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話加班唔返黎食，唔好留飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有"},{"pid":"6b50de2219f411ae92b9ba45fb8a4f7c031ad05d","tid":299774,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話加班唔返黎食，唔好留飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e888fa7c9061d33832e4c12cc305dc80ffa54ec","tid":299774,"uid":50621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:01:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真 我呀媽煮野真係唔得 <br />\n佢都有返工係一個禮拜煮二三日<br />\n試過阻止 話外賣啦 你咪煮啦<br />\n之後後果就當然佢發好大脾氣<br />\n成個月比佢係咁唸經 話我不孝 佢死左屎都無得食<br />\n想請教各位巴絲如何拒絕呀媽煮飯帶婉轉同唔不孝？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不孝就點做都係架啦，無辦法<br />\n<br />\n利申以前都有 D 野阿媽煮得難食，又係煮完迫我食。大個左好多年之後先脫離陰影食番"},{"pid":"23dc49f269a7beb9ebb5e895ccd4085289bb318d","tid":299774,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:01:57.000Z","msg":"等緊神回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e18347dfd00c5420e9d8b9f39b03061d9f164a8","tid":299774,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:03:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算啦 今晚都係解決唔到問題<br />\n因為在兩分鐘前 我呀媽已經開爐</blockquote><br />\n好似有排搞"},{"pid":"997104e258d297b614f6f7bde04887da58b9ef94","tid":299774,"uid":50621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:04:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>請好好珍惜有住家飯你食嘅日子</blockquote><br />\n收皮啦 又係家庭和諧扮撚曬野既人 唔知扮知出乜撚野聲</blockquote><br />\n孝順同唔想食飯真係要分開黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我呀媽係事業型女性 無煮飯習慣<br />\n近年先由肥媽啲食平d學下野 <br />\n我都唔明跟足點解可以差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好簡單，跟佢煮，本身都要識煮先<br />\n<br />\n佢買 D 食材唔係你求其買果 D<br />\n個湯料多過水，點跟"},{"pid":"9421eb1fc7ab73f7a88ae9e6e4ed85a81787c5cc","tid":299774,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>算啦 今晚都係解決唔到問題<br />\n因為在兩分鐘前 我呀媽已經開爐</blockquote><br />\n好似有排搞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無飯圖"},{"pid":"be7b579277cdbd73ef2416a7ce0835eb7d367bd4","tid":299774,"uid":50621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>教佢煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點夠薑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢d野點難食先 如果純粹調味唔得 咪同佢講返 等佢下次識調節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲野十次有九次生 雞同豬係廚房搞成粒半鐘都有血 點睇 佢識煮既餸 我計埋炒菜都係10道都比多<br />\n調味就一定啦 肥媽又無教清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔熟就真係唔食得，話佢聽會有蟲<br />\n<br />\n唔識整既話，半個鐘調味都未掂，搞半個鐘點會食得"},{"pid":"6f40dd8bc3eba1089a0211d4caafa28adecbdd5a","tid":299774,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:08:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>請好好珍惜有住家飯你食嘅日子</blockquote><br />\n收皮啦 又係家庭和諧扮撚曬野既人 唔知扮知出乜撚野聲</blockquote><br />\n孝順同唔想食飯真係要分開黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我呀媽係事業型女性 無煮飯習慣<br />\n近年先由肥媽啲食平d學下野 <br />\n我都唔明跟足點解可以差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好簡單，跟佢煮，本身都要識煮先<br />\n<br />\n佢買 D 食材唔係你求其買果 D<br />\n個湯料多過水，點跟</blockquote><br />\n最基本 煮下菜心 白肉 應該唔伏得去邊<br />\n一係叫你老母煮簡單啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ae184fc89ae754b9394c579fc69ec4ee20ed18","tid":299774,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>算啦 今晚都係解決唔到問題<br />\n因為在兩分鐘前 我呀媽已經開爐</blockquote><br />\n好似有排搞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 